2003-12-27  kichik

	* Contrib/VPatch/GenPat.exe, Contrib/VPatch/Readme.html,
	Contrib/VPatch/Source/GenPat/GenPat2.dpr,
	Contrib/VPatch/Source/GenPat/PatchGenerator.pas,
