	* Contrib/Modern UI/Changelog.txt, Contrib/Modern UI/Readme.html,
	Contrib/Modern UI/System.nsh, Contrib/Modern UI/ioSpecial.ini,
	Contrib/Modern UI/Language files/Default.nsh, Contrib/Modern
